ed3dfeb5-ec5e-4670-ae6a-bfb1512b4cd8.title: Note
ed3dfeb5-ec5e-4670-ae6a-bfb1512b4cd8.text: This tree is when interacting with the door with the basement

99a65bdf-e190-498b-b3f5-bc4d4833711a.title: Note
99a65bdf-e190-498b-b3f5-bc4d4833711a.text: head_mourner shares same dialogue generic tree

507a92db-634d-493b-b2d0-7249e0beac7d.title: Mourner
507a92db-634d-493b-b2d0-7249e0beac7d.text:
Hmmm, how did you get over here? You're not one of
this rabble. Ah well, you'll have to stay. Can't risk you
going back now.

options.text: I haven't got the plague though...
I'm looking for a woman named Elena.

b1bdfa4a-cba5-4f35-b6be-d648f4f01ad5.title: Mourner
b1bdfa4a-cba5-4f35-b6be-d648f4f01ad5.text:
We're working for King Lathas of East Ardougne. He
has tasked us with containing the accursed plague
sweeping West Ardougne.

790b6cbb-339d-47cf-9db8-b8f06d67d81d.title: Mourner
790b6cbb-339d-47cf-9db8-b8f06d67d81d.text:
We also do our best to ease these people's suffering.
We're nicknamed mourners because we spend a lot of
time at plague victim funerals, no one else is allowed to
risk attending.

d2df987f-a4c1-47a8-9750-32b2ea4d33b5.title: Mourner
d2df987f-a4c1-47a8-9750-32b2ea4d33b5.text:
It's a demanding job, and we get little thanks from the
people here.

5ce2bfe3-a4ad-433d-a644-f0a3bb031a6f.title: Note
5ce2bfe3-a4ad-433d-a644-f0a3bb031a6f.text:
mourner in black clothes, behind the townhall,
holding a vial.

3f6d9e4b-5b5f-48f0-bb9b-e719f7e2482c.title: <player>
3f6d9e4b-5b5f-48f0-bb9b-e719f7e2482c.text: I haven't got the plague though...

5260f8b3-1a39-44f6-8dd0-2f9896ea26f9.title: Mourner
5260f8b3-1a39-44f6-8dd0-2f9896ea26f9.text:
Can't risk you being a carrier. That protective clothing
you have isn't regulation issue. It won't meet safety
standards.

4c6f1b25-7c2b-439d-abd3-3878604f0d73.title: <player>
4c6f1b25-7c2b-439d-abd3-3878604f0d73.text: I'm looking for a woman named Elena.

65c9b0bb-88ee-41ae-9d7e-749970a584d2.title: Mourner
65c9b0bb-88ee-41ae-9d7e-749970a584d2.text:
Ah yes, I've heard of her. A healer I believe. She must
be mad coming over here voluntarily.

404c2eb2-d65f-4199-a42a-598a324a9aef.title: Mourner
404c2eb2-d65f-4199-a42a-598a324a9aef.text:
I hear rumours she has probably caught the plague
now. Very tragic, a stupid waste of life.

da05f1f6-7043-4bfa-9a95-951df02a5ea0.text:
The door won't open.
You notice a black cross on the door.

04e5bb41-f160-49e1-99b0-5debbe86a956.title: Mourner
04e5bb41-f160-49e1-99b0-5debbe86a956.text:
I'd stand away from there. That black cross means that
house has been touched by the plague.
